&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#bf616a;&quot;&gt;No&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; existing data file found. Starting fresh.
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;
