&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;i-heard-you-liked-loaders&quot;&gt;I Heard You Liked Loaders&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;I hope you like mine :)&lt;&#x2F;em&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Download the loader
&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;metaproblems.com&#x2F;d8fdeee664c1699c80687aca2873f974&#x2F;loader&quot;&gt;here&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;em&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yeah. “Loaders”. I definitely know what’s meant in this context.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Anyway…&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Courtesy of &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;binary.ninja&#x2F;free&#x2F;&quot;&gt;BinaryNinja&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre data-lang=&quot;c&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#2b303b;color:#c0c5ce;&quot; class=&quot;language-c &quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-c&quot; data-lang=&quot;c&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;int64_t &lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#8fa1b3;&quot;&gt;main&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;()
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;{
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#b48ead;&quot;&gt;void&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;* fsbase;
