&lt;p&gt;The initial part contains an anti-debugging check, specifically checking for
&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;x64.syscall.sh&#x2F;&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;ptrace&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre data-lang=&quot;as&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#2b303b;color:#c0c5ce;&quot; class=&quot;language-as &quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-as&quot; data-lang=&quot;as&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;MOV EAX,&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#d08770;&quot;&gt;00000065
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;SYSCALL
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Using &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;pwndbg&#x2F;pwndbg&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;pwndbg&#x2F;pwndbg&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;, it’s a little more clear:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre data-lang=&quot;as&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#2b303b;color:#c0c5ce;&quot; class=&quot;language-as &quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-as&quot; data-lang=&quot;as&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt; ► &lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#d08770;&quot;&gt;0x7ffff7fbf000&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    mov    edi, &lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#d08770;&quot;&gt;1&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;             EDI =&amp;gt; &lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#d08770;&quot;&gt;1
