&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Our customer believes that something suspicious was going on in their
network. Can you save the day and figure out what the attacked did?&lt;&#x2F;em&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Here’s a
