&lt;h2 id=&quot;where-we-jmping&quot;&gt;Where We JMPing&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Quick, we need to pick a place to JMP to! Can your tremendous strategy get
us the win?&lt;&#x2F;em&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
